{"tid":2458934,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"歐盟對華制裁　中國駐德大使向德方提出嚴正交涉","createTime":"2021-03-23T23:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-24T00:35:01.000Z","uid":230530,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cca8f728670c3aa433fb311ccf58b234da819bc1","tid":2458934,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T23:56:39.000Z","msg":"歐盟就新疆問題制裁中國後，中國駐德國大使吳懇向德方提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n吳懇當地周二緊急約見德國外交部國務秘書貝爾格，就歐盟外長會議藉口所謂新疆人權問題作出單邊對華制裁決定，向德方提出嚴正交涉，並通報中方反制措施。<br />\n<br />\n吳懇強調，今次事件完全是歐方挑起，中方必須回應。中方敦促包括德方在內的歐方，立即停止和糾正錯誤做法，避免進一步損害雙方互信與合作。"},{"pid":"65fd6305abf36544fa7146c05b73c1c870ece0fa","tid":2458934,"uid":324602,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:01:32.000Z","msg":"一切責任全在...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2b4e95af8c665418727821d2793b78f80cfd87","tid":2458934,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:21:33.000Z","msg":"唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c104e9414fad0f3709fae1cdb4a2968f789d32","tid":2458934,"uid":151074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:35:01.000Z","msg":"China all talk no action"}]}